WEBVTT

1
00:01:53.214 --> 00:01:55.280
          (Breathing)

2
00:02:07.945 --> 00:02:10.812
     (Varys) YOU'VE SEEN
     BETTER DAYS. MY LORD.

3
00:02:10.881 --> 00:02:12.480
                 ANOTHER VISIT ?

4
00:02:14.851 --> 00:02:16.952
                 IT SEEMS YOU'RE
                 MY LAST FRIEND.

5
00:02:17.020 --> 00:02:20.555
NO. NO. MANY
STILL LOVE YOU.

6
00:02:20.624 --> 00:02:24.742
SANSA CAME TO COURT
THIS MORNING TO PLEAD
FOR YOUR LIFE.

7
00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:29.264
            ON HER KNEES
            BEGGING FOR ME. HM !

8
00:02:29.350 --> 00:02:31.483
               DID YOU LAUGH
               WITH THE OTHERS ?

9
00:02:31.552 --> 00:02:35.187
YOU DO ME WRONG. MY LORD.
YOUR BLOOD IS THE
LAST THING I WANT.

10
00:02:35.255 --> 00:02:37.189
                  I DON'T KNOW
                  WHAT YOU WANT.

11
00:02:37.257 --> 00:02:38.907
                I'VE GIVEN UP
                TRYING TO GUESS.

12
00:02:42.396 --> 00:02:45.296
WHEN I WAS
STILL A BOY...

13
00:02:45.365 --> 00:02:48.467
BEFORE THEY CUT
MY BALLS OFF WITH
A HOT KNIFE...

14
00:02:48.535 --> 00:02:52.204
I TRAVELED WITH A GROUP OF
ACTORS THROUGH THE FREE CITIES.

15
00:02:53.607 --> 00:02:56.725
    THEY TAUGHT ME THAT EACH
    MAN HAS A ROLE TO PLAY.

16
00:02:56.794 --> 00:02:59.510
THE SAME IS
TRUE AT COURT.

17
00:02:59.579 --> 00:03:01.913
I AM THE MASTER
OF WHISPERERS.

18
00:03:01.982 --> 00:03:06.418
MY ROLE IS TO
BE SLY. OBSEQUIOUS
AND WITHOUT SCRUPLES.

19
00:03:06.487 --> 00:03:08.487
I'M A GOOD ACTOR.
MY LORD.

20
00:03:08.556 --> 00:03:11.873
              HUH. CAN YOU FREE
              ME FROM THIS PIT ?

21
00:03:11.942 --> 00:03:13.976
            I COULD.

22
00:03:14.044 --> 00:03:15.978
         BUT WILL I ?

23
00:03:16.046 --> 00:03:17.912
             NO.
                        (Laughs)

24
00:03:17.981 --> 00:03:19.982
AS I SAID.
I'M NO HERO.

25
00:03:20.067 --> 00:03:21.867
              WHAT DO YOU WANT ?
              TELL ME.

26
00:03:21.936 --> 00:03:24.903
     NO RIDDLES. NO STORIES.
     TELL ME. WHAT DO YOU WANT ?

27
00:03:26.874 --> 00:03:28.606
            PEACE.

28
00:03:28.675 --> 00:03:31.042
DID YOU KNOW THAT YOUR
SON IS MARCHING SOUTH...

29
00:03:31.111 --> 00:03:34.746
WITH AN ARMY OF NORTHMEN ?
LOYAL LAD.

30
00:03:34.815 --> 00:03:37.182
FIGHTING FOR HIS
FATHER'S FREEDOM.

31
00:03:37.251 --> 00:03:38.250
            ROBB ?

32
00:03:39.587 --> 00:03:41.386
                HE'S JUST A BOY.

33
00:03:41.455 --> 00:03:43.755
BOYS HAVE BEEN
CONQUERORS BEFORE.

34
00:03:43.824 --> 00:03:47.926
BUT THE MAN GIVING CERSEI
SLEEPLESS NIGHTS
IS THE KING'S--

35
00:03:47.995 --> 00:03:50.395
THE LATE KING'S
BROTHER.

36
00:03:50.464 --> 00:03:53.298
LORD STANNIS HAS THE
BEST CLAIM TO THE THRONE.

37
00:03:53.366 --> 00:03:56.602
HE IS A PROVEN BATTLE
COMMANDER AND HE IS
UTTERLY WITHOUT MERCY.

38
00:03:56.670 --> 00:04:01.139
        STANNIS BARATHEON IS
        ROBERT'S TRUE HEIR. THE
        THRONE IS HIS BY RIGHTS.

39
00:04:01.208 --> 00:04:02.774
          (Varys tuts)

40
00:04:02.843 --> 00:04:05.777
     SANSA PLEADED SO
     SWEETLY FOR YOUR LIFE.

41
00:04:05.846 --> 00:04:07.929
      IT WOULD BE A SHAME
      TO THROW IT AWAY.

42
00:04:09.483 --> 00:04:11.550
       CERSEI IS NO FOOL.

43
00:04:11.618 --> 00:04:14.986
     SHE KNOWS A TAME WOLF
     IS MORE USE TO HER
     THAN A DEAD ONE.

44
00:04:15.055 --> 00:04:17.456
             YOU WANT ME TO
             SERVE THE WOMAN WHO
             MURDERED MY KING...

45
00:04:17.524 --> 00:04:20.391
           WHO BUTCHERED MY MEN.
           WHO CRIPPLED MY SON ?

46
00:04:20.461 --> 00:04:22.427
       I WANT YOU TO
       SERVE THE REALM !

47
00:04:22.496 --> 00:04:25.213
TELL THE QUEEN
YOU WILL CONFESS
YOUR VILE TREASON...

48
00:04:25.299 --> 00:04:27.398
TELL YOUR SON TO LAY
DOWN HIS SWORD...

49
00:04:27.468 --> 00:04:30.585
AND PROCLAIM JOFFREY
AS THE TRUE HEIR.

50
00:04:32.555 --> 00:04:36.642
CERSEI KNOWS YOU
AS A MAN OF HONOR.

51
00:04:36.710 --> 00:04:38.610
IF YOU GIVE HER THE
PEACE SHE NEEDS...

52
00:04:38.679 --> 00:04:40.979
AND PROMISE TO CARRY HER
SECRET TO YOUR GRAVE...

53
00:04:41.047 --> 00:04:43.331
I BELIEVE SHE WILL ALLOW
YOU TO TAKE THE BLACK...

54
00:04:43.400 --> 00:04:47.001
AND LIVE OUT YOUR DAYS ON
THE WALL WITH YOUR BROTHER
AND YOUR BASTARD SON.

55
00:04:47.070 --> 00:04:48.420
                      (Chuckles)

56
00:04:48.489 --> 00:04:50.905
               YOU THINK MY LIFE
               IS SOME PRECIOUS
               THING TO ME ?

57
00:04:52.509 --> 00:04:55.844
              THAT I WOULD TRADE
              MY HONOR FOR A FEW
              MORE YEARS OF...

58
00:04:55.912 --> 00:04:57.511
                       OF WHAT ?

59
00:05:02.452 --> 00:05:04.152
                    YOU GREW UP
                    WITH ACTORS.

60
00:05:06.090 --> 00:05:08.823
               YOU LEARNED THEIR
               CRAFT AND YOU
               LEARNT IT WELL.

61
00:05:10.127 --> 00:05:12.060
                  BUT I GREW UP
                  WITH SOLDIERS.

62
00:05:14.932 --> 00:05:17.516
            I LEARNED HOW TO
            DIE A LONG TIME AGO.

63
00:05:20.487 --> 00:05:21.753
PITY.

64
00:05:23.440 --> 00:05:25.006
SUCH A PITY.

65
00:05:31.581 --> 00:05:33.965
WHAT OF YOUR DAUGHTER'S
LIFE. MY LORD ?

66
00:05:34.034 --> 00:05:36.601
IS THAT A PRECIOUS
THING TO YOU ?

67
00:05:40.741 --> 00:05:42.007
        (Water dripping)

68
00:05:51.034 --> 00:05:52.200
            (Cawing)

69
00:05:58.842 --> 00:06:00.141
        (Arrow whooshes)

70
00:06:18.045 --> 00:06:20.879
IT'S A BIRTHDAY MESSAGE
TO HIS GRAND-NIECE WALDA.

71
00:06:20.948 --> 00:06:23.048
           OR SO WALDER FREY
           WOULD HAVE YOU THINK.

72
00:06:23.116 --> 00:06:26.050
  KEEP SHOOTING THEM DOWN.
  WE CAN'T RISK LORD WALDER...

73
00:06:26.119 --> 00:06:27.902
SENDING WORD OF YOUR MOVEMENTS
TO THE LANNISTERS.

74
00:06:27.971 --> 00:06:30.989
   HE'S GRANDFATHER'S BANNERMAN.
   WE CAN'T EXPECT HIS SUPPORT ?

75
00:06:31.058 --> 00:06:34.960
   (Greatjon) EXPECT NOTHING
   OF WALDER FREY AND YOU'LL
   NEVER BE SURPRISED.

76
00:06:35.028 --> 00:06:36.261
LOOK.

77
00:06:38.331 --> 00:06:40.131
(Robb) FATHER ROTS IN A DUNGEON.

78
00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:43.251
            HOW LONG BEFORE
            THEY TAKE HIS HEAD ?

79
00:06:43.320 --> 00:06:45.453
              WE NEED TO CROSS
              THE TRIDENT AND WE
              NEED TO DO IT NOW.

80
00:06:45.521 --> 00:06:48.039
 JUST MARCH UP TO HIS GATES
 AND TELL HIM YOU'RE CROSSING.

81
00:06:48.108 --> 00:06:51.092
   WE'VE GOT FIVE TIMES HIS
   NUMBERS. YOU CAN TAKE
   THE TWINS IF YOU HAVE TO.

82
00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:54.562
    (Greatjon) NOT IN TIME.
    TYWIN LANNISTER MARCHES
    NORTH AS WE SPEAK.

83
00:06:54.631 --> 00:06:57.415
   THE FREYS HAVE HELD THE
   CROSSING FOR 600 YEARS...

84
00:06:57.484 --> 00:07:00.652
AND FOR 600 YEARS THEY
HAVE NEVER FAILED TO
EXACT THEIR TOLL.

85
00:07:00.721 --> 00:07:03.020
           HAVE MY HORSE SADDLED
           AND READY.

86
00:07:03.089 --> 00:07:06.241
ENTER THE TWINS ALONE
AND HE'LL SELL YOU TO
THE LANNISTERS AS HE LIKES.

87
00:07:06.309 --> 00:07:09.177
   OR THROW YOU IN A DUNGEON.
   OR SLIT YOUR THROAT.

88
00:07:11.898 --> 00:07:14.899
            MY FATHER WOULD DO
            WHATEVER IT TOOK TO
            SECURE OUR CROSSING.

89
00:07:14.968 --> 00:07:16.134
               WHATEVER IT TOOK.

90
00:07:17.370 --> 00:07:19.003
               IF I'M GOING TO
               LEAD THIS ARMY...

91
00:07:19.072 --> 00:07:21.939
              I CAN'T HAVE
              OTHER MEN DOING MY
              BARGAINING FOR ME.

92
00:07:22.008 --> 00:07:23.108
            I AGREE.

93
00:07:25.145 --> 00:07:26.478
          I'LL GO.
      (Theon) YOU CAN'T !

94
00:07:26.546 --> 00:07:28.829
    I HAVE KNOWN LORD WALDER
    SINCE I WAS A GIRL.

95
00:07:28.898 --> 00:07:30.865
    HE WOULD NEVER HARM ME.

96
00:07:30.934 --> 00:07:33.451
(Greatjon) UNLESS THERE
WAS A PROFIT IN IT.

97
00:07:39.492 --> 00:07:41.026
       WHAT DO YOU WANT ?

98
00:07:41.094 --> 00:07:43.128
IT IS A GREAT PLEASURE
TO SEE YOU AGAIN...

99
00:07:43.196 --> 00:07:44.696
AFTER SO MANY YEARS.
MY LORD.

100
00:07:44.765 --> 00:07:46.531
         OH. SPARE ME.

101
00:07:46.600 --> 00:07:50.719
    YOUR BOY'S TOO PROUD TO
    COME BEFORE ME HIMSELF.

102
00:07:50.787 --> 00:07:52.854
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO DO WITH YOU ?

103
00:07:52.923 --> 00:07:56.007
  FATHER. YOU FORGET YOURSELF.
  LADY STARK IS HERE...

104
00:07:56.075 --> 00:08:00.945
WHO ASKED YOU ? YOU'RE NOT
LORD FREY YET. NOT UNTIL I DIE.

105
00:08:01.014 --> 00:08:03.281
DO I LOOK DEAD TO YOU ?
      FATHER. PLEASE--

106
00:08:03.350 --> 00:08:06.067
   I NEED LESSONS IN COURTESY
   FROM YOU. BASTARD ?

107
00:08:06.136 --> 00:08:08.686
     YOUR MOTHER WOULD
     STILL BE A MILKMAID...

108
00:08:08.755 --> 00:08:11.138
     IF I HADN'T SQUIRTED
     YOU INTO HER BELLY.

109
00:08:15.278 --> 00:08:18.163
       ALL RIGHT.
       YOU COME FORWARD.

110
00:08:27.808 --> 00:08:29.807
        (Smacking kiss)

111
00:08:29.876 --> 00:08:32.310
THERE. NOW THAT I'VE
OBSERVED THE COURTESIES...

112
00:08:32.379 --> 00:08:35.780
PERHAPS MY SONS WILL DO ME THE
HONOR OF SHUTTING THEIR MOUTHS.

113
00:08:41.204 --> 00:08:43.237
              IS THERE SOMEWHERE
              WE CAN TALK ?

114
00:08:43.306 --> 00:08:45.323
WE'RE TALKING RIGHT NOW.

115
00:08:49.346 --> 00:08:50.911
             FINE.

116
00:08:50.980 --> 00:08:53.464
OUT ! ALL OF YOU !

117
00:09:03.677 --> 00:09:05.309
             OH !
YOU TOO.

118
00:09:12.635 --> 00:09:14.802
YOU SEE THAT ?

119
00:09:14.871 --> 00:09:16.971
FIFTEEN. SHE IS.

120
00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:18.806
A LITTLE FLOWER.

121
00:09:20.610 --> 00:09:23.611
AND HER HONEY'S ALL MINE.
(Chuckles)

122
00:09:25.649 --> 00:09:28.783
I'M SURE SHE WILL
GIVE YOU MANY SONS.

123
00:09:28.851 --> 00:09:31.952
         HUH. YOUR FATHER DIDN'T
         COME TO THE WEDDING.

124
00:09:32.021 --> 00:09:33.988
HE IS QUITE ILL. MY LORD.

125
00:09:34.057 --> 00:09:37.258
           HUH. DIDN'T COME TO
           THE LAST ONE. EITHER.

126
00:09:37.327 --> 00:09:39.227
         OR THE ONE BEFORE THAT.

127
00:09:41.130 --> 00:09:43.164
            YOUR FAMILY HAS
            ALWAYS PISSED ON ME.

128
00:09:43.233 --> 00:09:46.184
MY LORD. I...
             DON'T DENY IT.
             YOU KNOW IT'S TRUE.

129
00:09:46.253 --> 00:09:50.705
        THE FINE LORD TULLY
        WOULD NEVER MARRY ANY
        OF HIS CHILDREN TO MINE.

130
00:09:50.773 --> 00:09:53.775
I'M SURE THERE WERE REASONS...
          I DIDN'T NEED REASONS.

131
00:09:53.844 --> 00:09:56.711
     I NEEDED TO GET RID OF
     SONS AND DAUGHTERS.

132
00:09:56.780 --> 00:09:58.729
   YOU SEE HOW THEY PILE UP ?

133
00:10:02.618 --> 00:10:04.152
              WHY ARE YOU HERE ?

134
00:10:06.289 --> 00:10:07.755
TO ASK YOU...

135
00:10:07.824 --> 00:10:10.959
TO OPEN YOUR GATES.
MY LORD...

136
00:10:11.027 --> 00:10:14.779
SO MY SON AND HIS BANNERMEN
MAY CROSS THE TRIDENT
AND BE ON THEIR WAY.

137
00:10:14.848 --> 00:10:17.965
          WHY SHOULD I LET HIM ?
IF YOU COULD CLIMB
YOUR OWN BATTLEMENTS...

138
00:10:18.034 --> 00:10:21.585
YOU WOULD SEE THAT
HE HAS 20.000 MEN
OUTSIDE YOUR WALLS.

139
00:10:21.655 --> 00:10:25.089
            THEY'LL BE 20.000
            CORPSES WHEN TYWIN
            LANNISTER GETS HERE.

140
00:10:25.158 --> 00:10:27.541
                   DON'T TRY AND
                   FRIGHTEN ME.
                   LADY STARK.

141
00:10:27.610 --> 00:10:30.061
        YOUR HUSBAND'S IN A CELL
        BENEATH THE RED KEEP...

142
00:10:30.130 --> 00:10:33.031
       AND YOUR SON'S GOT NO FUR
       TO KEEP HIS BALLS WARM.

143
00:10:33.099 --> 00:10:35.500
YOU SWORE AN OATH
TO MY FATHER.

144
00:10:35.568 --> 00:10:38.637
       OH. YES.
       I SAID SOME WORDS.

145
00:10:38.705 --> 00:10:42.740
 AND I SWORE OATHS TO THE CROWN
 TOO. IF I REMEMBER RIGHT.

146
00:10:42.809 --> 00:10:47.212
       JOFFREY'S KING NOW. WHICH
       MAKES YOUR BOY AND HIS
       CORPSES-TO-BE...

147
00:10:47.280 --> 00:10:49.464
      NOTHING BUT REBELS.
      IT SEEMS TO ME.

148
00:10:50.833 --> 00:10:53.201
    IF I HAD THE SENSE
    THE GODS GAVE A FISH...

149
00:10:53.269 --> 00:10:54.986
     I'D HAND YOU BOTH OVER
     TO THE LANNISTERS.

150
00:10:55.055 --> 00:10:59.640
WHY DON'T YOU ?
           STARK. TULLY.
           LANNISTER. BARATHEON.

151
00:11:01.378 --> 00:11:02.877
      GIVE ME ONE GOOD REASON...

152
00:11:02.946 --> 00:11:06.330
     WHY I SHOULD WASTE A SINGLE
     THOUGHT ON ANY OF YOU ?

153
00:11:06.399 --> 00:11:09.851
     (Man) AND...ENGAGE !
        (Wind howls)

154
00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:11.352
          (Door slams)

155
00:11:11.421 --> 00:11:13.988
            WHEN DOES AEMON
            THINK YOU'LL BE ABLE
            TO USE THAT HAND ?

156
00:11:14.057 --> 00:11:16.290
SOON. HE SAYS.
                           GOOD.

157
00:11:17.794 --> 00:11:20.211
                 YOU'LL BE READY
                 FOR THIS. THEN.

158
00:11:20.280 --> 00:11:24.865
            I THOUGHT A WOLF WAS
            MORE APPROPRIATE FOR
            YOU THAN A BEAR...

159
00:11:26.302 --> 00:11:28.519
                  SO I HAD A NEW
                  POMMEL MADE.

160
00:11:28.588 --> 00:11:30.705
           IT'S CALLED LONGCLAW.

161
00:11:30.773 --> 00:11:33.641
               WORKS AS WELL FOR
               A WOLF AS A BEAR.
               I THINK.

162
00:11:44.504 --> 00:11:45.870
THIS IS VALYRIAN STEEL.

163
00:11:47.724 --> 00:11:51.709
       IT WAS MY FATHER'S SWORD.
       HIS FATHER BEFORE HIM.

164
00:11:51.778 --> 00:11:55.229
               THE MORMONTS HAVE
               CARRIED IT FOR
               FIVE CENTURIES.

165
00:11:55.298 --> 00:11:58.065
                IT WAS MEANT FOR
                MY SON JORAH.

166
00:11:58.134 --> 00:12:00.267
             HE BROUGHT DISHONOR
             TO OUR HOUSE...

167
00:12:00.337 --> 00:12:03.170
           BUT HE HAD THE GRACE
           TO LEAVE THE SWORD...

168
00:12:03.239 --> 00:12:06.324
                  BEFORE HE FLED
                  FROM WESTEROS.

169
00:12:06.393 --> 00:12:08.025
          MY LORD. YOU HONOR ME.
          BUT I CAN'T--

170
00:12:08.095 --> 00:12:09.727
          OH. YOU CAN.

171
00:12:09.796 --> 00:12:11.596
         AND YOU WILL.

172
00:12:11.664 --> 00:12:15.600
     I WOULDN'T BE STANDING
     HERE IF IT WASN'T FOR
     YOU AND YOUR BEAST.

173
00:12:15.668 --> 00:12:18.452
       A BLOODY DEAD MAN
       TRIED TO KILL ME.

174
00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:24.758
              SO YOU'LL TAKE IT.
              I'LL HEAR NO
              MORE ABOUT IT.

175
00:12:24.828 --> 00:12:26.945
            IS THAT UNDERSTOOD ?
YES. MY LORD.

176
00:12:27.013 --> 00:12:28.629
                          RIGHT.

177
00:12:28.698 --> 00:12:30.215
                NOW. DON'T THINK
                THIS MEANS...

178
00:12:30.283 --> 00:12:33.651
    I APPROVE OF THIS NONSENSE
    WITH YOU AND ALLISER THORNE.

179
00:12:34.721 --> 00:12:36.821
           THAT'S A MAN'S SWORD.

180
00:12:36.890 --> 00:12:38.456
                IT'LL TAKE A MAN
                TO WIELD IT.

181
00:12:39.726 --> 00:12:41.609
I'LL APOLOGIZE TO
SER ALLISER TONIGHT.

182
00:12:41.678 --> 00:12:45.129
            NO. YOU WON'T.
            I SENT HIM TO KING'S
            LANDING YESTERDAY.

183
00:12:45.198 --> 00:12:49.216
              THE HAND THAT YOUR
              WOLF TORE OFF THAT
              THING'S WRIST...

184
00:12:49.302 --> 00:12:52.670
             I'VE. UH. ORDERED
             THORNE TO LAY IT AT
             THE FEET OF THIS...

185
00:12:52.738 --> 00:12:54.605
                       BOY KING.

186
00:12:54.674 --> 00:12:56.874
           THAT SHOULD GET YOUNG
           JOFFREY'S ATTENTION.

187
00:12:58.544 --> 00:13:03.797
         AND IT. UH. PUTS
         A THOUSAND LEAGUES
         BETWEEN YOU AND THORNE.

188
00:13:03.866 --> 00:13:06.451
               NOW GO AND
               PUT YOUR SWORD
               SOMEWHERE SAFE...

189
00:13:06.520 --> 00:13:08.987
         AND BRING ME MY SUPPER.

190
00:13:09.055 --> 00:13:10.905
YES. MY LORD.

191
00:13:22.151 --> 00:13:24.252
           WELL DONE.
           WELL DONE.

192
00:13:26.489 --> 00:13:28.155
     YOU EARNED THAT. SNOW.

193
00:13:32.295 --> 00:13:33.561
           WELL DONE.

194
00:13:38.735 --> 00:13:40.200
   GO ON. LET'S HAVE A LOOK.

195
00:13:40.269 --> 00:13:42.620
AT WHAT ?
             (Grenn) THE SWORD !
             SHOW US THE SWORD.

196
00:13:42.689 --> 00:13:45.673
     (All) SWORD ! SWORD !
     SWORD ! SWORD !

197
00:13:45.742 --> 00:13:49.042
    SWORD ! SWORD !
    SWORD ! SWORD ! SWORD !

198
00:13:49.111 --> 00:13:50.578
      (Laughter. cheering)

199
00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:55.950
      LET'S HAVE A LOOK.
          PISS OFF.

200
00:13:56.036 --> 00:13:57.635
  (Laughter. excited chatter)

201
00:13:59.039 --> 00:14:01.556
   COME ON. I WANT TO HAVE A
   LOOK AT IT IN THE LIGHT.

202
00:14:04.927 --> 00:14:06.860
      (Pyp) GIVE IT HERE !

203
00:14:06.929 --> 00:14:08.862
          WHAT IS IT ?

204
00:14:08.931 --> 00:14:10.965
             I...
      LOOK AT ITS EYES.

205
00:14:11.033 --> 00:14:12.467
GIVE IT.
            I CAN'T.

206
00:14:13.503 --> 00:14:15.169
                YOU CAN'T WHAT ?

207
00:14:15.238 --> 00:14:16.471
             I...

208
00:14:18.174 --> 00:14:20.774
I'M REALLY NOT
SUPPOSED TO SAY.

209
00:14:20.843 --> 00:14:23.511
              AND YET YOU REALLY
              WANT TO SAY.

210
00:14:23.580 --> 00:14:25.646
                    YOU WANT TO
                    SAY THAT-- ?

211
00:14:28.935 --> 00:14:31.685
THERE WAS A RAVEN.

212
00:14:31.754 --> 00:14:34.188
I READ THE MESSAGE
TO MAESTER AEMON.

213
00:14:36.092 --> 00:14:38.009
IT'S YOUR BROTHER ROBB.

214
00:14:38.077 --> 00:14:39.877
             WHAT ?

215
00:14:39.946 --> 00:14:41.245
                WHAT ABOUT HIM ?

216
00:14:42.882 --> 00:14:44.481
HE'S HEADING SOUTH.

217
00:14:44.551 --> 00:14:45.816
TO WAR.

218
00:14:48.555 --> 00:14:52.322
ALL HIS BANNERMEN
HAVE RALLIED TO HIS SIDE.
THEY'LL KEEP HIM SAFE.

219
00:14:53.760 --> 00:14:55.492
              I SHOULD BE THERE.

220
00:14:57.797 --> 00:14:59.396
           I SHOULD BE WITH HIM.

221
00:15:00.533 --> 00:15:02.299
    (Hoofbeats approaching)

222
00:15:14.364 --> 00:15:16.915
 IF WE DO THAT.
 THEY'LL NEVER GET BACK ACROSS.

223
00:15:18.501 --> 00:15:20.267
         (Robb) WELL ?

224
00:15:20.336 --> 00:15:23.237
       WHAT DID HE SAY ?

225
00:15:23.305 --> 00:15:25.773
LORD WALDER HAS
GRANTED YOUR CROSSING.

226
00:15:27.693 --> 00:15:30.711
 HIS MEN ARE YOURS. AS WELL.
        (Greatjon) HUH.

227
00:15:30.780 --> 00:15:33.230
LESS THE 400 HE
WILL KEEP HERE TO
HOLD THE CROSSING...

228
00:15:33.299 --> 00:15:34.599
AGAINST ANY WHO
WOULD PURSUE YOU.

229
00:15:34.667 --> 00:15:36.100
        WHAT DOES HE
        WANT IN RETURN ?

230
00:15:36.168 --> 00:15:40.421
YOU WILL BE TAKING ON HIS SON
OLYVAR AS YOUR PERSONAL SQUIRE.

231
00:15:40.490 --> 00:15:42.623
    HE EXPECTS A KNIGHTHOOD
    IN GOOD TIME.

232
00:15:42.692 --> 00:15:43.858
          FINE. FINE.

233
00:15:45.528 --> 00:15:46.694
             AND ?

234
00:15:48.380 --> 00:15:50.247
AND ARYA...

235
00:15:50.316 --> 00:15:54.185
WILL MARRY HIS SON WALDRON
WHEN THEY BOTH COME OF AGE.

236
00:15:54.254 --> 00:15:56.520
  SHE WON'T BE HAPPY ABOUT THAT.
             HM.

237
00:16:00.626 --> 00:16:01.975
                           AND ?

238
00:16:03.112 --> 00:16:04.278
             AND...

239
00:16:05.748 --> 00:16:07.615
  WHEN THE FIGHTING IS DONE...

240
00:16:09.886 --> 00:16:11.986
       YOU WILL MARRY ONE
       OF HIS DAUGHTERS.

241
00:16:13.006 --> 00:16:15.206
WHICHEVER YOU PREFER.

242
00:16:15.275 --> 00:16:18.659
   HE HAS A NUMBER HE
   THINKS WILL BE...SUITABLE.

243
00:16:18.728 --> 00:16:19.927
             I SEE.

244
00:16:22.365 --> 00:16:24.832
DID YOU GET A LOOK
AT HIS DAUGHTERS ?
                    (Snickering)

245
00:16:24.901 --> 00:16:26.467
I DID.

246
00:16:27.503 --> 00:16:28.803
             AND ?

247
00:16:30.205 --> 00:16:31.705
           ONE WAS--

248
00:16:37.664 --> 00:16:39.163
        DO YOU CONSENT ?

249
00:16:40.366 --> 00:16:43.050
                  CAN I REFUSE ?
   NOT IF YOU WANT TO CROSS.

250
00:16:46.956 --> 00:16:48.623
                 THEN I CONSENT.

251
00:16:51.944 --> 00:16:53.193
                      (Chuckles)

252
00:17:23.776 --> 00:17:25.092
            (Cawing)

253
00:17:34.153 --> 00:17:36.320
SAM SAID YOU
WANTED TO SEE ME ?

254
00:17:36.389 --> 00:17:38.789
                   I DID INDEED.

255
00:17:38.858 --> 00:17:41.709
       PERHAPS YOU WOULD BE
       KIND ENOUGH TO ASSIST ME.

256
00:17:45.181 --> 00:17:50.584
TELL ME. DID YOU EVER
WONDER WHY THE MEN OF
THE NIGHT'S WATCH...

257
00:17:50.653 --> 00:17:53.754
TAKE NO WIVES AND
FATHER NO CHILDREN ?

258
00:17:53.823 --> 00:17:55.523
              NO.

259
00:17:55.591 --> 00:17:58.109
     SO THEY WILL NOT LOVE.

260
00:17:58.177 --> 00:18:01.862
   LOVE IS THE DEATH OF DUTY.

261
00:18:01.931 --> 00:18:05.799
      IF THE DAY SHOULD EVER
      COME WHEN YOUR LORD FATHER
      WAS FORCED TO CHOOSE...

262
00:18:05.868 --> 00:18:08.235
                BETWEEN HONOR ON
                THE ONE HAND...

263
00:18:08.304 --> 00:18:10.804
              AND THOSE HE LOVES
              ON THE OTHER...

264
00:18:10.873 --> 00:18:12.906
              WHAT WOULD HE DO ?

265
00:18:12.975 --> 00:18:14.475
HE...

266
00:18:14.544 --> 00:18:18.178
HE WOULD DO WHATEVER WAS
RIGHT. NO MATTER WHAT.

267
00:18:18.247 --> 00:18:22.517
              THEN LORD STARK IS
              ONE MAN IN 10.000.

268
00:18:22.585 --> 00:18:25.235
                  MOST OF US ARE
                  NOT SO STRONG.

269
00:18:25.304 --> 00:18:27.137
                WHAT IS HONOR...

270
00:18:27.206 --> 00:18:29.907
                  COMPARED TO A
                  WOMAN'S LOVE ?

271
00:18:29.976 --> 00:18:32.443
             AND WHAT IS DUTY...

272
00:18:32.512 --> 00:18:36.079
   AGAINST THE FEEL OF A
   NEWBORN SON IN YOUR ARMS ?

273
00:18:36.149 --> 00:18:38.582
          OR A BROTHER'S SMILE ?

274
00:18:43.005 --> 00:18:44.488
SAM TOLD YOU.

275
00:18:44.557 --> 00:18:46.574
                WE'RE ALL HUMAN.

276
00:18:46.659 --> 00:18:49.893
               OH. WE ALL DO OUR
               DUTY WHEN THERE'S
               NO COST TO IT.

277
00:18:49.962 --> 00:18:52.095
          HONOR COMES EASY THEN.

278
00:18:52.849 --> 00:18:54.382
                          YET...

279
00:18:54.450 --> 00:18:56.417
              SOONER OR LATER...

280
00:18:56.486 --> 00:18:58.485
          IN EVERY MAN'S LIFE...

281
00:18:58.554 --> 00:19:01.622
            THERE COMES A DAY
            WHEN IT IS NOT EASY.

282
00:19:01.691 --> 00:19:04.759
                   A DAY WHEN HE
                   MUST CHOOSE.

283
00:19:06.863 --> 00:19:08.679
AND THIS IS MY DAY ?

284
00:19:08.747 --> 00:19:10.798
IS THAT WHAT
YOU'RE SAYING ?

285
00:19:10.867 --> 00:19:14.034
              OH. IT HURTS. BOY.
              OH. YES.

286
00:19:14.103 --> 00:19:17.121
                         I KNOW.
YOU DO NOT KNOW.

287
00:19:18.858 --> 00:19:20.090
         NO ONE KNOWS.

288
00:19:23.145 --> 00:19:24.645
           I MAY BE A BASTARD...

289
00:19:24.714 --> 00:19:27.247
         BUT HE IS MY FATHER
         AND ROBB IS MY BROTHER.

290
00:19:27.316 --> 00:19:28.583
           (Chuckles)

291
00:19:31.538 --> 00:19:35.873
THE GODS WERE CRUEL
WHEN THEY SAW FIT
TO TEST MY VOWS.

292
00:19:35.941 --> 00:19:37.825
THEY WAITED
TILL I WAS OLD.

293
00:19:39.462 --> 00:19:43.497
WHAT COULD I DO WHEN
THE RAVENS BROUGHT THE
NEWS FROM THE SOUTH...

294
00:19:43.566 --> 00:19:46.033
THE RUIN OF MY HOUSE.
THE DEATH OF MY FAMILY ?

295
00:19:46.102 --> 00:19:48.568
I WAS HELPLESS...

296
00:19:48.638 --> 00:19:50.805
BLIND. FRAIL.

297
00:19:53.275 --> 00:19:55.142
             BUT...

298
00:19:55.210 --> 00:19:58.779
   WHEN I HEARD THEY HAD
   KILLED MY BROTHER'S SON...

299
00:19:58.848 --> 00:20:00.981
      AND HIS POOR SON...

300
00:20:01.050 --> 00:20:02.499
       AND THE CHILDREN !

301
00:20:02.569 --> 00:20:05.002
EVEN THE LITTLE CHILDREN.

302
00:20:07.373 --> 00:20:08.656
                   WHO ARE YOU ?

303
00:20:10.760 --> 00:20:14.595
MY FATHER WAS MAEKAR...

304
00:20:14.664 --> 00:20:16.813
THE FIRST OF HIS NAME.

305
00:20:16.882 --> 00:20:21.152
MY BROTHER AEGON
REIGNED AFTER HIM...

306
00:20:21.220 --> 00:20:24.138
WHEN I HAD REFUSED
THE THRONE.

307
00:20:24.206 --> 00:20:27.691
AND HE WAS FOLLOWED
BY HIS SON AERYS...

308
00:20:27.760 --> 00:20:30.744
WHOM THEY CALLED
THE MAD KING.

309
00:20:30.813 --> 00:20:34.498
         YOU'RE AEMON TARGARYEN.

310
00:20:34.567 --> 00:20:37.268
I'M A MAESTER
OF THE CITADEL...

311
00:20:37.336 --> 00:20:41.622
BOUND IN SERVICE
TO CASTLE BLACK AND
THE NIGHT'S WATCH.

312
00:20:44.510 --> 00:20:49.513
I WILL NOT TELL YOU...
TO STAY OR GO.

313
00:20:49.582 --> 00:20:52.249
YOU MUST MAKE THAT
CHOICE YOURSELF...

314
00:20:52.318 --> 00:20:55.869
AND LIVE WITH IT FOR
THE REST OF YOUR DAYS.

315
00:20:59.409 --> 00:21:00.808
AS I HAVE.

316
00:21:27.369 --> 00:21:28.786
             DROGO.

317
00:21:30.172 --> 00:21:32.255
           (Mutters)

318
00:21:32.325 --> 00:21:33.424
            (Grunts)

319
00:22:33.686 --> 00:22:35.402
         HYAH ! HYAH !

320
00:22:55.574 --> 00:22:59.443
  (Kevan) OUR SCOUTS TELL
  US THE STARK HOST HAS MOVED
  SOUTH FROM THE TWINS...

321
00:22:59.512 --> 00:23:01.912
WITH LORD FREY'S LEVIES IN TOW.

322
00:23:01.980 --> 00:23:04.515
  THEY'RE A DAY'S MARCH NORTH.

323
00:23:04.583 --> 00:23:07.017
    THE BOY MAY LACK
    EXPERIENCE AND SENSE...

324
00:23:07.085 --> 00:23:10.471
      BUT HE DOES HAVE A
      CERTAIN MINDLESS...

325
00:23:10.540 --> 00:23:13.106
PROVINCIAL COURAGE.
                             AH.

326
00:23:16.612 --> 00:23:18.879
   OH. DO CONTINUE.
   DIDN'T MEAN TO INTERRUPT.

327
00:23:18.948 --> 00:23:21.431
   I DO HOPE YOUR SAVAGES ARE
   GOING TO BE OF SOME USE...

328
00:23:21.500 --> 00:23:23.550
     OTHERWISE WE'VE WASTED
     GOOD STEEL ON THEM.

329
00:23:23.619 --> 00:23:27.070
  THE GREAT HAIRY ONE INSISTED
  HE MUST HAVE TWO BATTLEAXES.

330
00:23:27.139 --> 00:23:29.640
HEAVY BLACK STEEL. DOUBLE-SIDED.

331
00:23:29.709 --> 00:23:31.609
SHAGGA LIKES AXES.

332
00:23:31.677 --> 00:23:36.447
   WHEN THE BATTLE COMMENCES.
   YOU AND YOUR WILDLINGS
   WILL BE IN THE VANGUARD.

333
00:23:36.515 --> 00:23:38.081
                  THE VANGUARD ?
           MM-HM.

334
00:23:38.150 --> 00:23:40.800
            ME AND THE TRIBESMEN
            ON THE FRONT LINES ?

335
00:23:40.869 --> 00:23:43.153
      (Kevan) THEY DO SEEM
      RATHER FEROCIOUS.

336
00:23:45.857 --> 00:23:47.625
      (Tyrion) FEROCIOUS ?

337
00:23:47.693 --> 00:23:52.429
         LAST NIGHT...A MOON
         BROTHER STABBED A STONE
         CROW OVER A SAUSAGE.

338
00:23:52.498 --> 00:23:56.266
         THREE STONE CROWS
         SEIZED THE MOON BROTHER
         AND OPENED HIS THROAT.

339
00:23:56.335 --> 00:23:59.019
BRONN MANAGED TO KEEP
SHAGGA FROM CHOPPING OFF
THE DEAD MAN'S COCK...

340
00:23:59.088 --> 00:24:03.307
WHICH WAS FORTUNATE.
BUT EVEN STILL. ULF IS
DEMANDING BLOOD MONEY...

341
00:24:03.375 --> 00:24:05.992
          WHICH SHAGGA AND
          GUNTHOR REFUSE TO PAY.

342
00:24:06.062 --> 00:24:09.246
WHEN SOLDIERS LACK
DISCIPLINE. THE FAULT LIES
WITH THEIR COMMANDER.

343
00:24:09.315 --> 00:24:10.981
    SURELY THERE ARE WAYS
    TO HAVE ME KILLED...

344
00:24:11.050 --> 00:24:12.816
       THAT WOULD BE LESS
       DETRIMENTAL TO
       THE WAR EFFORT.

345
00:24:12.884 --> 00:24:15.152
        THERE'LL BE NO
        MORE DISCUSSION
        ON THE MATTER.

346
00:24:20.609 --> 00:24:22.910
       IT APPEARS I'M NOT
       HUNGRY AFTER ALL.

347
00:24:22.995 --> 00:24:24.427
      EXCUSE ME. MY LORDS.

348
00:24:38.227 --> 00:24:40.794
WHERE DID YOU FIND
ONE SO PRETTY AT THIS HOUR ?

349
00:24:40.863 --> 00:24:43.664
I TOOK HER.
                      TOOK HER ?

350
00:24:43.732 --> 00:24:46.266
                     FROM WHOM ?
FROM. UH...

351
00:24:46.334 --> 00:24:49.436
SER--
WHAT'S HIS NAME ?

352
00:24:49.504 --> 00:24:52.139
I DON'T KNOW.
GINGER CUNT.
THREE TENTS DOWN.

353
00:24:52.208 --> 00:24:55.559
               AND HE DIDN'T
               HAVE ANYTHING
               TO SAY ABOUT IT ?

354
00:24:55.628 --> 00:24:57.194
HE SAID SOMETHING.

355
00:24:59.882 --> 00:25:03.850
WELL. THE ODDS OF ME
LIVING LONG ENOUGH
FOR HIM TO RETALIATE...

356
00:25:03.920 --> 00:25:05.402
HAVE JUST DROPPED
DRASTICALLY.

357
00:25:05.470 --> 00:25:07.538
WE'LL BE AT THE
VANGUARD TOMORROW.

358
00:25:10.676 --> 00:25:12.342
               OH. WELL. (Sighs)

359
00:25:13.895 --> 00:25:17.964
           I. UH...THINK I'LL GO
           AND FIND MYSELF ONE.

360
00:25:22.171 --> 00:25:23.953
WHO ARE YOU ?

361
00:25:24.022 --> 00:25:26.456
                 WHO WOULD YOU
                 LIKE ME TO BE ?

362
00:25:26.525 --> 00:25:28.258
WHAT DID YOUR
MOTHER CALL YOU ?

363
00:25:28.327 --> 00:25:31.461
             SHAE. WHAT DID YOUR
             MOTHER CALL YOU ?

364
00:25:31.531 --> 00:25:34.515
MY MOTHER DIED
GIVING BIRTH TO ME.

365
00:25:34.583 --> 00:25:38.469
          IS THAT WHY I'M HERE ?
          SO WE CAN TALK
          ABOUT OUR MOTHERS ?

366
00:25:38.537 --> 00:25:41.054
WHAT SORT OF ACCENT IS THAT ?
                        FOREIGN.

367
00:25:41.123 --> 00:25:42.740
             FOR...

368
00:25:44.710 --> 00:25:46.760
   WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME ?

369
00:25:46.829 --> 00:25:48.996
   WHAT DO I WANT FROM YOU ?

370
00:25:49.064 --> 00:25:52.116
(Sighs) I WANT YOU
TO SHARE MY TENT.

371
00:25:52.184 --> 00:25:55.202
I WANT YOU TO POUR MY WINE.
LAUGH AT MY JOKES...

372
00:25:55.270 --> 00:25:58.571
 RUB MY LEGS WHEN THEY'RE SORE
 AFTER A DAY'S RIDE.

373
00:25:58.640 --> 00:26:00.340
I WANT YOU TO
TAKE NO OTHER
MAN TO BED...

374
00:26:00.408 --> 00:26:02.009
FOR AS LONG AS
WE'RE TOGETHER.

375
00:26:02.078 --> 00:26:06.713
AND I WANT YOU TO FUCK
ME LIKE IT'S MY LAST
NIGHT IN THIS WORLD.

376
00:26:06.782 --> 00:26:08.849
WHICH IT MAY WELL BE.

377
00:26:08.917 --> 00:26:10.517
             AND WHAT DO I GET ?

378
00:26:10.603 --> 00:26:13.637
            ONE--
            SAFETY.

379
00:26:13.706 --> 00:26:17.424
NO ONE WILL HURT YOU
FOR AS LONG AS YOU'RE MINE.

380
00:26:17.493 --> 00:26:20.160
TWO--THE PLEASURE
OF MY COMPANY...

381
00:26:20.229 --> 00:26:22.896
WHICH I HAVE HEARD
IS SPECTACULAR.

382
00:26:22.964 --> 00:26:25.182
             WHO TOLD YOU THIS ?
             WOMEN YOU PAID ?

383
00:26:25.251 --> 00:26:27.684
AND THREE...

384
00:26:27.753 --> 00:26:31.071
MORE GOLD THAN YOU CAN SPEND
IF YOU LIVED A THOUSAND YEARS.

385
00:26:32.774 --> 00:26:34.741
DO YOU ACCEPT MY PROPOSAL ?

386
00:26:53.913 --> 00:26:57.181
       LET'S START WITH YOUR
       LAST NIGHT IN THIS WORLD.

387
00:27:16.502 --> 00:27:18.435
       DOTH... DOTHRAE...

388
00:27:29.731 --> 00:27:31.231
       (Jorah) KHALEESI.

389
00:27:31.300 --> 00:27:32.232
             COME.

390
00:27:34.870 --> 00:27:36.937
       HE'S VERY STRONG.

391
00:27:37.023 --> 00:27:39.723
       NO ONE UNDERSTANDS
       HOW STRONG HE IS.

392
00:27:54.573 --> 00:27:55.906
        (Daenerys gasps)

393
00:27:59.045 --> 00:28:02.562
HE WILL DIE TONIGHT. KHALEESI.
                       HE CAN'T.

394
00:28:02.631 --> 00:28:04.564
                HE CAN'T.
                I WON'T LET HIM.

395
00:28:04.633 --> 00:28:07.517
            EVEN A QUEEN DOESN'T
            HAVE THAT POWER.

396
00:28:10.622 --> 00:28:13.906
            WE MUST GO QUICKLY.
            I'VE HEARD THERE'S A
            GOOD PORT IN ASSHAI.

397
00:28:13.975 --> 00:28:18.095
      I WON'T LEAVE HIM.
    HE'S ALREADY GONE. KHALEESI.

398
00:28:18.163 --> 00:28:20.164
            DOTH...

399
00:28:20.232 --> 00:28:21.598
           EVEN IF...

400
00:28:24.036 --> 00:28:26.636
       EVEN IF HE DIES...

401
00:28:26.706 --> 00:28:29.123
       WHY WOULD I RUN ?

402
00:28:29.191 --> 00:28:33.777
I AM KHALEESI. AND MY...
MY SON WILL BE KHAL AFTER DROGO.

403
00:28:33.846 --> 00:28:37.014
    THIS ISN'T WESTEROS.
    WHERE MEN HONOR BLOOD.

404
00:28:37.083 --> 00:28:41.734
 HERE THEY ONLY HONOR STRENGTH.
 THERE WILL BE FIGHTING
 AFTER DROGO DIES.

405
00:28:41.803 --> 00:28:44.538
    WHOEVER WINS THAT FIGHT
    WILL BE THE NEW KHAL.

406
00:28:44.606 --> 00:28:46.673
   HE WON'T WANT ANY RIVALS.

407
00:28:46.741 --> 00:28:51.011
        YOUR BOY WILL BE PLUCKED
        FROM YOUR BREAST AND
        GIVEN TO THE DOGS.

408
00:28:52.614 --> 00:28:54.814
      I WON'T...LEAVE HIM.

409
00:29:05.460 --> 00:29:06.960
    THE WOUND HAS FESTERED.

410
00:30:07.756 --> 00:30:11.225
I THINK YOU SHOULD WEAR
YOUR ARMOR TONIGHT. SER.

411
00:30:11.293 --> 00:30:12.792
           I THINK YOU'RE RIGHT.

412
00:30:18.333 --> 00:30:22.352
   YOU'VE SAVED ME ONCE MORE.
   AND NOW YOU MUST SAVE HIM.

413
00:30:22.420 --> 00:30:24.654
HE'S BEYOND THE HEALER'S SKILLS.

414
00:30:24.723 --> 00:30:27.173
 ALL I CAN DO IS EASE HIS PATH.

415
00:30:27.243 --> 00:30:29.309
     SAVE HIM AND I WILL
     FREE YOU. I SWEAR IT.

416
00:30:30.762 --> 00:30:33.162
      YOU MUST KNOW A WAY.

417
00:30:33.231 --> 00:30:34.497
            SOME...

418
00:30:35.835 --> 00:30:37.117
          SOME MAGIC.

419
00:30:39.288 --> 00:30:41.921
       THERE IS A SPELL.

420
00:30:41.990 --> 00:30:44.074
SOME WOULD SAY
DEATH IS CLEANER.

421
00:30:54.286 --> 00:30:55.669
             DO IT.

422
00:30:56.822 --> 00:30:58.588
                       SAVE HIM.

423
00:30:58.657 --> 00:30:59.705
THERE IS A PRICE.

424
00:30:59.774 --> 00:31:01.457
              YOU'LL HAVE GOLD.
              WHATEVER YOU WANT.

425
00:31:01.526 --> 00:31:03.860
IT'S NOT A MATTER OF GOLD.
THIS IS BLOODMAGIC.

426
00:31:03.929 --> 00:31:05.896
ONLY DEATH PAYS FOR LIFE.

427
00:31:09.434 --> 00:31:11.051
           MY DEATH ?

428
00:31:11.120 --> 00:31:13.687
NO. NOT YOUR
DEATH. KHALEESI.

429
00:31:15.557 --> 00:31:17.156
BRING ME HIS HORSE.

430
00:31:29.020 --> 00:31:30.319
          (Whinnying)

431
00:31:40.799 --> 00:31:42.599
KHALEESI. DO NOT DO THIS THING.

432
00:31:42.667 --> 00:31:45.985
LET ME KILL THIS WITCH.
KILL HER AND YOU KILL YOUR KHAL.

433
00:31:46.054 --> 00:31:49.038
THIS IS BLOODMAGIC.
IT IS FORBIDDEN.

434
00:31:49.108 --> 00:31:52.758
      I AM YOUR KHALEESI.
      I TELL YOU WHAT
      IS FORBIDDEN.

435
00:31:52.827 --> 00:31:54.427
        (Recites spell)

436
00:32:03.255 --> 00:32:04.487
            GO. NOW.

437
00:32:04.556 --> 00:32:06.489
TAKE HER AND LEAVE.
UH-UH.

438
00:32:06.558 --> 00:32:07.858
           TAKE HER !

439
00:32:13.599 --> 00:32:17.567
  YOU MUST GO ALSO. LADY.
  ONCE I BEGIN TO SING.
  NO ONE MUST ENTER THE TENT.

440
00:32:17.636 --> 00:32:20.137
      THE DEAD WILL
      DANCE HERE TONIGHT.

441
00:32:33.585 --> 00:32:35.001
       NO ONE WILL ENTER.

442
00:32:37.055 --> 00:32:38.905
        (Recites spell)

443
00:32:43.545 --> 00:32:45.795
        (Horse thuds)
    BRING HIM BACK TO ME.

444
00:32:47.416 --> 00:32:49.181
           (Singing)

445
00:33:02.397 --> 00:33:04.096
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE ?

446
00:33:04.165 --> 00:33:06.499
             I HAVE TO SAVE HIM.

447
00:33:06.568 --> 00:33:09.869
WE COULD HAVE BEEN 10 MILES
AWAY FROM HERE BY NOW.
ON THE WAY TO ASSHAI.

448
00:33:09.938 --> 00:33:12.806
YOU WOULD HAVE BEEN SAFE.
           (Grunts)

449
00:33:12.874 --> 00:33:14.474
      (Demonic shrieking)

450
00:33:28.707 --> 00:33:30.506
           (Grunts)
          KHALEESI !

451
00:33:34.546 --> 00:33:37.296
           (Sobbing)

452
00:33:37.383 --> 00:33:39.282
      (Singing continues)

453
00:34:15.270 --> 00:34:16.469
                  ARE YOU HURT ?

454
00:34:16.538 --> 00:34:17.570
         THE BABY...
             HMM ?

455
00:34:17.639 --> 00:34:19.305
         ...IS COMING.

456
00:34:19.374 --> 00:34:21.741
             FETCH THE MIDWIVES.
THEY WILL NOT COME.

457
00:34:21.810 --> 00:34:23.242
THEY SAY SHE IS CURSED.

458
00:34:24.612 --> 00:34:26.813
            THEY'LL COME OR I'LL
            HAVE THEIR HEADS.

459
00:34:26.882 --> 00:34:29.015
           (Groans)
THE WITCH--

460
00:34:29.084 --> 00:34:31.517
SHE CAN BRING BABY.
I HEAR HER SAY SO.

461
00:34:33.105 --> 00:34:35.205
  (Singing. demonic bellowing)

462
00:34:48.837 --> 00:34:50.837
 (Singing. bellowing continues)

463
00:34:55.127 --> 00:34:56.859
(Shae) ARE YOU
IN AGONY. MY LION ?

464
00:34:56.929 --> 00:35:00.196
                             NO.
YOU LOOK LIKE YOU'RE IN AGONY.

465
00:35:00.265 --> 00:35:02.999
THE FIRE IS BURNING
YOUR PRETTY SOFT SKIN.

466
00:35:06.505 --> 00:35:08.037
                            AH !
          (Laughter)

467
00:35:09.858 --> 00:35:12.442
        DAMN YOU. WOMAN.
        ARE YOU IMMUNE TO PAIN ?

468
00:35:12.511 --> 00:35:14.861
JUST USED TO IT.
             DRINK.

469
00:35:16.865 --> 00:35:18.581
             (Tyrion) LET'S PLAY
             A NEW GAME.

470
00:35:20.168 --> 00:35:22.836
THERE'S A BRAAVOSI KNIFE
GAME I COULD TEACH YOU.

471
00:35:22.904 --> 00:35:26.039
 DOES IT INVOLVE THE POTENTIAL
 FOR LOSING FINGERS ?

472
00:35:26.108 --> 00:35:28.675
       NOT IF YOU WIN.
                            NO !

473
00:35:28.744 --> 00:35:32.128
 NO FIRE GAMES. NO KNIFE GAMES.

474
00:35:32.197 --> 00:35:36.282
 LET'S DO SOMETHING I'M GOOD AT.
WHAT ARE YOU GOOD AT ?

475
00:35:36.351 --> 00:35:38.317
          I HAPPEN TO BE A GREAT
          JUDGE OF CHARACTER.

476
00:35:38.386 --> 00:35:40.670
THIS SOUNDS LIKE A BORING GAME.
                       IT'S NOT.

477
00:35:40.738 --> 00:35:44.874
    HERE'S HOW IT WORKS--I MAKE
    A STATEMENT ABOUT YOUR PAST.

478
00:35:44.942 --> 00:35:48.110
        IF I'M RIGHT. YOU DRINK.
        IF I'M WRONG. I DRINK.

479
00:35:48.180 --> 00:35:51.097
           AND NO LYING. I'LL
           KNOW IF YOU'RE LYING.

480
00:35:51.166 --> 00:35:53.065
I DON'T WANT TO
PLAY THIS GAME.

481
00:35:53.134 --> 00:35:55.101
                    FINE.
                    BRONN FIRST.

482
00:35:59.724 --> 00:36:01.491
           YOUR FATHER BEAT YOU.

483
00:36:07.165 --> 00:36:09.082
   BUT MY MOTHER HIT HARDER.

484
00:36:12.621 --> 00:36:15.154
       YOU KILLED YOUR FIRST MAN
       BEFORE YOU WERE 12.

485
00:36:15.223 --> 00:36:16.522
IT WAS A WOMAN.

486
00:36:20.328 --> 00:36:21.594
    SHE SWUNG AN AXE AT ME.

487
00:36:23.415 --> 00:36:24.897
               YOU'VE BEEN NORTH
               OF THE WALL.

488
00:36:28.453 --> 00:36:30.019
WHAT BROUGHT
YOU UP THERE ?

489
00:36:31.723 --> 00:36:34.573
WORK.
                          AND...

490
00:36:34.643 --> 00:36:38.027
          YOU ONCE LOVED A WOMAN
          MANY YEARS AGO. BUT IT
          TURNED OUT BADLY...

491
00:36:38.096 --> 00:36:39.779
            SO YOU'VE NEVER LET
            YOURSELF LOVE AGAIN.

492
00:36:41.783 --> 00:36:43.650
            OH. WAIT. THAT'S ME.

493
00:36:47.355 --> 00:36:50.173
        YOUR TURN. MY MYSTERIOUS
        FOREIGN BEAUTY.

494
00:36:50.241 --> 00:36:51.841
I DON'T WANT TO PLAY.

495
00:36:51.910 --> 00:36:55.628
                 IT'S FUN !
                 LOOK AT THE FUN
                 WE'RE HAVING.

496
00:36:59.233 --> 00:37:00.383
        YOUR MOTHER WAS A WHORE.

497
00:37:02.320 --> 00:37:03.386
DRINK.

498
00:37:10.045 --> 00:37:12.178
                      ALL RIGHT.

499
00:37:12.247 --> 00:37:15.749
     YOUR FATHER LEFT THE FAMILY
     WHEN YOU WERE VERY YOUNG.
     NEVER TO RETURN.

500
00:37:15.817 --> 00:37:18.084
DRINK.

501
00:37:18.153 --> 00:37:21.771
         AND WE'VE ESTABLISHED
         THE RULES ABOUT LYING ?
DRINK !

502
00:37:24.342 --> 00:37:26.376
        (Bronn pours)
             MM.

503
00:37:28.446 --> 00:37:30.012
                 YOU WANTED A
                 DIFFERENT LIFE.

504
00:37:30.081 --> 00:37:32.832
         YOU CAME FROM SOMEWHERE
         AND YOU WANTED
         TO BE ELSEWHERE.

505
00:37:32.901 --> 00:37:35.418
  THE WHOLE SHIT-STAINED WORLD
  COULD DRINK OFF THAT ONE.

506
00:37:35.487 --> 00:37:37.854
                 SO. SPECIFICS--

507
00:37:37.923 --> 00:37:41.458
   YOU WANTED TO BE ELSEWHERE.
   BUT HOW WOULD YOU GET THERE ?

508
00:37:41.526 --> 00:37:45.328
             I DON'T BELIEVE THE
             LIFE OF THE SILENT
             SISTERS IS FOR YOU.

509
00:37:45.397 --> 00:37:49.064
            SO...WHAT'S A
            LOWBORN GIRL TO DO ?

510
00:37:52.237 --> 00:37:53.936
DRINK.

511
00:37:56.808 --> 00:37:58.824
                 ARE YOU SURE...
            DRINK !

512
00:38:04.098 --> 00:38:07.950
AND DON'T TALK ABOUT MY
MOTHER AND FATHER EVER...

513
00:38:08.019 --> 00:38:10.637
OR I WILL CARVE YOUR
EYES FROM YOUR HEAD.

514
00:38:15.010 --> 00:38:17.844
              MY DEAR LADY. IF I
              HAVE OFFENDED YOU.
              I APOLOGIZE.

515
00:38:19.130 --> 00:38:20.162
           MY TURN.

516
00:38:20.215 --> 00:38:22.315
                     FINE. FINE.

517
00:38:22.383 --> 00:38:24.684
                       ASK AWAY.

518
00:38:24.753 --> 00:38:27.687
            TRY TO PENETRATE THE
            ENIGMA THAT IS ME.

519
00:38:27.755 --> 00:38:30.739
WHO WERE YOU IN LOVE WITH ?
  THAT'S NOT HOW THE GAME WORKS.

520
00:38:30.808 --> 00:38:33.192
I DON'T CARE THE
WAY THE GAME WORKS.

521
00:38:33.261 --> 00:38:36.162
      OUR LORD HERE
      USED TO BE MARRIED.

522
00:38:36.231 --> 00:38:38.364
           MARRIED ?
         HOW DID YOU HEAR THAT ?

523
00:38:38.432 --> 00:38:42.368
    YOU HEAR LOTS OF THINGS
    PLAYING DICE WITH
    LANNISTER SOLDIERS.

524
00:38:44.288 --> 00:38:46.973
         ANOTHER NIGHT. PERHAPS.

525
00:38:47.042 --> 00:38:50.476
       NOT ANOTHER NIGHT.
       THIS NIGHT.

526
00:38:50.545 --> 00:38:52.077
      IT'S NOT A PLEASANT STORY.

527
00:38:54.182 --> 00:38:55.882
OH. MAYBE I WILL CRY.

528
00:38:55.951 --> 00:38:57.400
     I'M GUESSING THE LADY AND I

529
00:38:57.469 --> 00:39:00.403
     CAN TELL MORE UNPLEASANT
     STORIES THAN YOUR LORDSHIP.

530
00:39:02.540 --> 00:39:03.773
             SO...

531
00:39:08.012 --> 00:39:10.079
           I WAS 16.

532
00:39:10.148 --> 00:39:13.783
MY BROTHER JAIME
AND I WERE RIDING.
WHEN WE HEARD A SCREAM.

533
00:39:13.851 --> 00:39:19.038
SHE RAN OUT ONTO THE ROAD.
CLOTHES HALF TORN OFF.
WITH TWO MEN ON HER HEELS.

534
00:39:19.107 --> 00:39:22.976
      JAIME SCARED AWAY THE
      MEN EASILY ENOUGH. WHILE
      I WRAPPED HER IN MY CLOAK.

535
00:39:23.061 --> 00:39:24.928
          SHE WAS TOO SCARED TO
          SEND OFF ON HER OWN...

536
00:39:24.996 --> 00:39:27.613
           SO WHILE JAIME HUNTED
           DOWN THE RAPERS...

537
00:39:27.682 --> 00:39:30.016
        I TOOK HER TO THE
        NEAREST INN AND FED HER.

538
00:39:30.101 --> 00:39:32.569
HER NAME WAS TYSHA.

539
00:39:32.637 --> 00:39:34.837
SHE WAS A
WHEELWRIGHT'S ORPHAN.

540
00:39:34.906 --> 00:39:37.139
AND SHE WAS HUNGRY.

541
00:39:37.208 --> 00:39:40.510
TOGETHER WE FINISHED
OFF THREE CHICKENS
AND A FLAGON OF WINE.

542
00:39:40.579 --> 00:39:44.814
IMPOSSIBLE AS IT SEEMS.
THERE WAS A TIME WHEN I
WAS UNACCUSTOMED TO WINE.

543
00:39:44.883 --> 00:39:48.051
I FORGOT HOW AFRAID
I WAS AROUND GIRLS...

544
00:39:48.119 --> 00:39:51.520
   HOW I WAS ALWAYS WAITING
   FOR THEM TO LAUGH AT ME OR...

545
00:39:51.590 --> 00:39:52.955
        LOOK AWAY EMBARRASSED...

546
00:39:53.024 --> 00:39:55.724
        OR ASK ME ABOUT MY TALL.
        HANDSOME BROTHER.

547
00:39:55.793 --> 00:39:59.328
           I FORGOT ABOUT
           EVERYTHING BUT TYSHA.

548
00:39:59.397 --> 00:40:02.264
             AND SOMEHOW I FOUND
             MYSELF IN HER BED.

549
00:40:02.317 --> 00:40:05.218
      FOR THREE CHICKENS.
      I SHOULD HOPE SO.

550
00:40:05.287 --> 00:40:08.387
IT DIDN'T LAST LONG.
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT
THE HELL I WAS DOING.

551
00:40:08.456 --> 00:40:10.857
BUT SHE WAS GOOD TO ME.

552
00:40:10.925 --> 00:40:13.860
SHE KISSED ME AFTERWARDS AND...

553
00:40:13.928 --> 00:40:15.327
       SANG ME A SONG.

554
00:40:17.048 --> 00:40:21.484
            AND BY MORNING I WAS
            DEEP ENOUGH IN LOVE
            TO ASK FOR HER HAND.

555
00:40:21.552 --> 00:40:23.986
     A FEW LIES.
     A FEW GOLD COINS.
     ONE DRUNKEN SEPTON...

556
00:40:24.055 --> 00:40:25.754
    AND THERE YOU HAVE IT--
    MAN AND WIFE.

557
00:40:27.525 --> 00:40:32.294
    FOR A FORTNIGHT ANYWAY.
    UNTIL THE SEPTON SOBERED
    UP AND TOLD MY FATHER.

558
00:40:32.363 --> 00:40:35.047
    WELL. I IMAGINE THAT
    WAS THE END OF ALL THAT.

559
00:40:35.116 --> 00:40:36.482
NOT QUITE.

560
00:40:37.852 --> 00:40:40.719
FIRST. MY FATHER HAD JAIME
TELL ME THE TRUTH.

561
00:40:42.657 --> 00:40:44.523
THE GIRL WAS A
WHORE. YOU SEE.

562
00:40:46.360 --> 00:40:51.447
     JAIME HAD ARRANGED THE
     WHOLE THING--THE ROAD.
     THE RAPERS. ALL OF IT.

563
00:40:51.516 --> 00:40:53.866
             HE THOUGHT IT WAS
             TIME I HAD A WOMAN.

564
00:40:56.103 --> 00:40:58.104
AFTER MY BROTHER CONFESSED...

565
00:40:59.491 --> 00:41:01.391
MY FATHER BROUGHT IN MY WIFE...

566
00:41:01.459 --> 00:41:03.292
AND GAVE HER TO HIS GUARDS.

567
00:41:04.863 --> 00:41:07.697
     HE PAID HER WELL--
     A SILVER FOR EACH MAN.

568
00:41:07.766 --> 00:41:12.451
    HOW MANY WHORES COMMAND
    THAT KIND OF PRICE ?

569
00:41:12.520 --> 00:41:15.988
  HE BROUGHT ME INTO THE
  BARRACKS AND MADE ME WATCH.

570
00:41:16.057 --> 00:41:19.425
      BY THE END. SHE HAD
      SO MUCH SILVER...

571
00:41:19.511 --> 00:41:22.211
     THAT THE COINS
     WERE SLIPPING
     THROUGH HER FINGERS...

572
00:41:22.279 --> 00:41:24.313
  AND ROLLING ON TO THE FLOOR.

573
00:41:28.169 --> 00:41:30.937
I WOULD HAVE KILLED THE
MAN WHO DID THAT TO ME.

574
00:41:32.107 --> 00:41:34.073
           YOU SHOULD HAVE KNOWN
           SHE WAS A WHORE.

575
00:41:35.076 --> 00:41:36.909
                        REALLY ?

576
00:41:36.978 --> 00:41:39.478
                 I WAS 16. DRUNK
                 AND IN LOVE.

577
00:41:39.547 --> 00:41:41.280
A GIRL WHO WAS
ALMOST RAPED...

578
00:41:41.349 --> 00:41:44.283
DOESN'T INVITE
ANOTHER MAN INTO HER
BED TWO HOURS LATER.

579
00:41:45.987 --> 00:41:49.589
    AS I SAID.
    I WAS YOUNG AND STUPID.

580
00:41:52.243 --> 00:41:54.743
YOU ARE STILL YOUNG AND STUPID.

581
00:42:03.621 --> 00:42:05.070
           (Kissing)

582
00:42:11.762 --> 00:42:13.062
     (Galloping hoofbeats)

583
00:42:18.336 --> 00:42:19.569
             HYAH !

584
00:42:26.978 --> 00:42:29.545
         (Horse neighs)

585
00:42:29.614 --> 00:42:31.080
       (Distant shouting)

586
00:42:35.020 --> 00:42:36.636
          (Clattering)

587
00:42:36.704 --> 00:42:40.239
 WHAT IS IT ? WHAT DO YOU WANT ?
YOU'RE SLEEPING THROUGH THE WAR.

588
00:42:40.308 --> 00:42:43.042
             WHAT ?
THEY STOLE A NIGHT'S
MARCH ON US.

589
00:42:43.111 --> 00:42:45.394
THEY'RE A MILE NORTH.

590
00:42:45.463 --> 00:42:47.764
        GET MY SQUIRE !
YOU DON'T HAVE A SQUIRE.

591
00:42:50.368 --> 00:42:52.234
IF I DIE. WEEP FOR ME.

592
00:42:53.671 --> 00:42:56.972
             YOU'LL BE DEAD.
             HOW WILL YOU KNOW ?

593
00:43:03.247 --> 00:43:04.763
I'LL KNOW.

594
00:43:07.051 --> 00:43:08.985
       WATCH OUT ! MOVE !

595
00:43:09.721 --> 00:43:11.387
        OUT OF THE WAY !

596
00:43:11.456 --> 00:43:13.456
          MOVE ASIDE !
          (Neighing)

597
00:43:19.764 --> 00:43:21.163
           STAY LOW.

598
00:43:22.266 --> 00:43:23.833
                      STAY LOW ?

599
00:43:23.902 --> 00:43:26.302
IF YOU'RE LUCKY.
NO ONE WILL NOTICE YOU.

600
00:43:26.370 --> 00:43:28.304
               I WAS BORN LUCKY.

601
00:43:31.409 --> 00:43:33.743
    TRIBESMEN OF THE VALE...

602
00:43:33.812 --> 00:43:35.411
         GATHER ROUND !

603
00:43:36.831 --> 00:43:39.315
         STONE CROWS !

604
00:43:39.383 --> 00:43:41.634
          BLACK EARS !
          BURNED MEN !

605
00:43:41.703 --> 00:43:44.354
        MOON BROTHERS !
   (Man) AND PAINTED DOGS !

606
00:43:44.422 --> 00:43:47.256
       AND PAINTED DOGS !
      (Men) PAINTED DOGS !

607
00:43:47.325 --> 00:43:50.242
     YOUR DOMINION OVER
     THE VALE BEGINS NOW !

608
00:43:50.328 --> 00:43:53.212
        ONWARD. TO CLAIM
        WHAT IS YOURS !

609
00:43:53.281 --> 00:43:55.431
     HALF MAN ! HALF MAN !

610
00:43:55.500 --> 00:43:58.868
  (All) HALF MAN ! HALF MAN !

611
00:43:58.937 --> 00:44:01.587
     HALF MAN ! HALF MAN !

612
00:44:01.655 --> 00:44:03.555
          TO BATTLE !

613
00:44:03.624 --> 00:44:05.091
           (Yelling)

614
00:44:21.425 --> 00:44:24.293
   (Horse neighing. echoes)

615
00:44:24.362 --> 00:44:25.962
        (Muffled shouts)

616
00:44:40.044 --> 00:44:41.444
        (Wagon rumbling)

617
00:44:46.050 --> 00:44:48.201
 (Bronn) YOU'RE A SHIT WARRIOR.

618
00:44:51.038 --> 00:44:53.322
          I'M ALIVE ?

619
00:44:53.391 --> 00:44:54.824
         YOU'RE ALIVE.

620
00:45:00.397 --> 00:45:02.047
          DID WE WIN ?

621
00:45:02.116 --> 00:45:04.833
WE WOULDN'T BE HAVING
THIS CONVERSATION IF WE DIDN'T.

622
00:45:04.903 --> 00:45:06.235
          (Screaming)

623
00:45:08.606 --> 00:45:10.639
       (Blades slashing)
       (Men screaming)

624
00:45:17.832 --> 00:45:19.932
      HOW DID OUR TRIBESMEN DO ?

625
00:45:21.636 --> 00:45:22.902
YEAH. GOOD.

626
00:45:24.872 --> 00:45:27.773
    (Tyrion) IT'S NICE TO
    SEE THEM GETTING ALONG.

627
00:45:27.841 --> 00:45:30.226
    (Tywin) YOU'RE WOUNDED.

628
00:45:30.294 --> 00:45:33.095
     GOOD OF YOU TO NOTICE.

629
00:45:33.164 --> 00:45:34.463
         I HEAR WE WON.

630
00:45:34.532 --> 00:45:37.917
  HUH ! THE SCOUTS WERE WRONG.

631
00:45:37.986 --> 00:45:40.603
     THERE WERE 2.000 STARK
     BANNERMEN. NOT 20.

632
00:45:41.906 --> 00:45:44.073
            DID WE GET THE STARK
            BOY. AT LEAST ?

633
00:45:44.142 --> 00:45:46.359
HE WASN'T HERE.

634
00:45:46.427 --> 00:45:48.194
                  WHERE WAS HE ?

635
00:45:48.263 --> 00:45:51.063
        WITH HIS OTHER
        18.000 MEN.

636
00:45:54.318 --> 00:45:56.018
      AND WHERE ARE THEY ?

637
00:46:06.580 --> 00:46:08.897
          WE SHOULD GO. MY LADY.
NO !

638
00:46:13.938 --> 00:46:15.204
           MY LADY !

639
00:46:17.541 --> 00:46:19.976
          (Neighing)
        HYAH ! HYAH !

640
00:46:48.873 --> 00:46:50.806
        (Pants. grunts)

641
00:46:50.875 --> 00:46:54.409
BY THE TIME THEY KNEW
WHAT WAS HAPPENING.
IT HAD ALREADY HAPPENED.

642
00:46:58.382 --> 00:47:02.518
     LADY STARK. I'D OFFER
     YOU MY SWORD. BUT I
     SEEM TO HAVE LOST IT.

643
00:47:02.586 --> 00:47:04.536
IT IS NOT YOUR SWORD I WANT.

644
00:47:06.007 --> 00:47:07.640
GIVE ME MY DAUGHTERS BACK.

645
00:47:07.709 --> 00:47:09.342
GIVE ME MY HUSBAND.

646
00:47:10.745 --> 00:47:12.244
             I'VE LOST THEM TOO.
             I'M AFRAID.

647
00:47:12.313 --> 00:47:14.830
  (Theon) KILL HIM. ROBB.
  SEND HIS HEAD TO HIS FATHER.

648
00:47:14.899 --> 00:47:17.533
     HE CUT DOWN TEN OF
     OUR MEN. YOU SAW HIM.

649
00:47:17.602 --> 00:47:19.735
HE'S MORE USE TO US
ALIVE THAN DEAD.

650
00:47:19.804 --> 00:47:21.987
    (Catelyn) TAKE HIM AWAY
    AND PUT HIM IN IRONS.

651
00:47:23.324 --> 00:47:25.507
     WE COULD END THIS
     WAR RIGHT NOW. BOY...

652
00:47:25.576 --> 00:47:27.642
    SAVE THOUSANDS OF LIVES.

653
00:47:27.711 --> 00:47:30.630
  YOU FIGHT FOR THE STARKS.
  I FIGHT FOR THE LANNISTERS.

654
00:47:30.698 --> 00:47:32.731
       SWORDS OR LANCES.
       TEETH. NAILS--

655
00:47:32.800 --> 00:47:36.451
      CHOOSE YOUR WEAPONS
      AND LET'S END THIS
      HERE AND NOW.

656
00:47:39.057 --> 00:47:43.092
IF WE DO IT YOUR WAY.
KINGSLAYER...YOU'D WIN.

657
00:47:47.114 --> 00:47:48.480
WE'RE NOT DOING
IT YOUR WAY.

658
00:47:50.484 --> 00:47:52.417
      (Greatjon) COME ON.
      PRETTY MAN.

659
00:47:52.486 --> 00:47:54.453
      (Laughter. cheering)

660
00:48:01.378 --> 00:48:03.946
I SENT 2.000 MEN TO
THEIR GRAVES TODAY.

661
00:48:04.015 --> 00:48:06.214
       THE BARDS WILL SING
       SONGS OF THEIR SACRIFICE.

662
00:48:06.283 --> 00:48:09.501
AYE. BUT THE DEAD
WON'T HEAR THEM.

663
00:48:16.326 --> 00:48:18.944
ONE VICTORY DOES NOT
MAKE US CONQUERORS.

664
00:48:20.798 --> 00:48:22.731
    DID WE FREE MY FATHER ?

665
00:48:23.934 --> 00:48:26.402
    DID WE RESCUE MY
    SISTERS FROM THE QUEEN ?

666
00:48:28.139 --> 00:48:31.607
     DID WE FREE THE NORTH
     FROM THOSE WHO WANT
     US ON OUR KNEES ?

667
00:48:36.981 --> 00:48:38.914
   THIS WAR IS FAR FROM OVER.

668
00:48:52.696 --> 00:48:54.130
         (Bell tolling)

669
00:49:10.465 --> 00:49:12.148
COULD I HAVE ONE ?

670
00:49:12.216 --> 00:49:13.999
A LEMON ONE...
OR ANY OF THEM.

671
00:49:14.068 --> 00:49:16.485
                  THREE COPPERS.

672
00:49:16.553 --> 00:49:19.571
HOW ABOUT A NICE FAT PIGEON ?
        OH. PISS OFF NOW. GO ON.

673
00:49:21.275 --> 00:49:24.176
DO YOU HAVE ANY STALE
ONES FROM YESTERDAY ?
OR ANY BURNT ONES ?

674
00:49:24.245 --> 00:49:25.944
                      PISS OFF !

675
00:49:33.103 --> 00:49:35.204
 HEY. WHERE'S EVERYONE GOING ?
 WHAT'S HAPPENING ?

676
00:49:35.273 --> 00:49:37.206
THEY'RE TAKING
HIM TO THE SEPT
OF BAELOR.

677
00:49:37.275 --> 00:49:39.274
             WHO ?
THE HAND OF THE KING.

678
00:50:14.578 --> 00:50:16.011
       (Crowd clamoring)

679
00:50:21.335 --> 00:50:22.968
    (Clamoring intensifies)

680
00:50:24.422 --> 00:50:25.588
           (Jeering)

681
00:50:46.911 --> 00:50:49.144
           TRAITOR !
           COWARD !

682
00:50:49.213 --> 00:50:51.313
     (Ned mutters) BAELOR.

683
00:50:51.382 --> 00:50:53.015
            BAELOR !

684
00:50:58.339 --> 00:51:00.306
      TRAITOR ! TRAITOR !

685
00:51:12.152 --> 00:51:13.418
       (Crowd quietens)

686
00:51:21.094 --> 00:51:23.379
      I AM EDDARD STARK...

687
00:51:23.448 --> 00:51:25.514
     LORD OF WINTERFELL...

688
00:51:25.583 --> 00:51:27.483
     AND HAND OF THE KING.

689
00:51:37.110 --> 00:51:39.511
     I COME BEFORE YOU TO
     CONFESS MY TREASON...

690
00:51:40.797 --> 00:51:42.665
 IN THE SIGHT OF GODS AND MEN.

691
00:51:44.668 --> 00:51:47.386
      I BETRAYED THE
      FAITH OF MY KING...

692
00:51:47.454 --> 00:51:49.421
       AND THE TRUST OF
       MY FRIEND ROBERT.

693
00:51:50.908 --> 00:51:54.243
     I SWORE TO PROTECT AND
     DEFEND HIS CHILDREN.

694
00:51:54.312 --> 00:51:56.462
       BUT BEFORE HIS
       BLOOD WAS COLD...

695
00:51:57.365 --> 00:52:00.182
 I PLOTTED TO MURDER HIS SON...

696
00:52:00.250 --> 00:52:02.818
AND SEIZE THE THRONE FOR MYSELF.

697
00:52:02.886 --> 00:52:04.402
      (Jeering. clamoring)

698
00:52:13.180 --> 00:52:19.084
    LET THE HIGH SEPTON AND
    BAELOR THE BLESSED BEAR
    WITNESS TO WHAT I SAY...

699
00:52:22.155 --> 00:52:23.555
      JOFFREY BARATHEON...

700
00:52:25.225 --> 00:52:27.325
     IS THE ONE TRUE HEIR
     TO THE IRON THRONE...

701
00:52:28.513 --> 00:52:30.963
        BY THE GRACE OF
        ALL THE GODS...

702
00:52:31.031 --> 00:52:33.331
 LORD OF THE SEVEN KINGDOMS...

703
00:52:33.400 --> 00:52:35.601
  AND PROTECTOR OF THE REALM.

704
00:52:35.670 --> 00:52:37.519
        (Crowd jeering)

705
00:52:37.588 --> 00:52:38.720
            (Gasps)

706
00:52:43.009 --> 00:52:45.711
       AS... AS WE SIN...

707
00:52:45.779 --> 00:52:47.530
        SO DO WE SUFFER.

708
00:52:47.582 --> 00:52:50.649
          THIS MAN HAS CONFESSED
          HIS CRIMES...

709
00:52:50.718 --> 00:52:53.802
       IN SIGHT OF GODS AND MEN.

710
00:52:53.870 --> 00:52:56.538
            THE GODS ARE JUST...

711
00:52:56.607 --> 00:53:00.108
              BUT BELOVED BAELOR
              TAUGHT US...

712
00:53:00.177 --> 00:53:02.944
                   THEY CAN ALSO
                   BE MERCIFUL.

713
00:53:06.100 --> 00:53:10.235
   WHAT IS TO BE DONE WITH
   THIS TRAITOR. YOUR GRACE ?

714
00:53:10.304 --> 00:53:11.987
      (Jeering. catcalls)

715
00:53:15.109 --> 00:53:18.209
         MY MOTHER WISHES ME
         TO LET LORD EDDARD
         JOIN THE NIGHT'S WATCH.

716
00:53:18.278 --> 00:53:20.679
     STRIPPED OF ALL TITLES
     AND POWERS...

717
00:53:20.747 --> 00:53:23.682
    HE WOULD SERVE THE REALM
    IN PERMANENT EXILE.

718
00:53:23.767 --> 00:53:28.020
      AND MY LADY SANSA...
      HAS BEGGED MERCY
      FOR HER FATHER.

719
00:53:32.493 --> 00:53:34.843
     BUT THEY HAVE THE
     SOFT HEARTS OF WOMEN.

720
00:53:36.213 --> 00:53:38.179
        SO LONG AS I AM
        YOUR KING...

721
00:53:38.249 --> 00:53:41.049
      TREASON SHALL NEVER
      GO UNPUNISHED.

722
00:53:42.119 --> 00:53:43.401
                     SER ILYN...

723
00:53:44.639 --> 00:53:45.837
             BRING ME HIS HEAD !

724
00:53:45.923 --> 00:53:48.040
            NO !
       (Crowd roars)

725
00:53:48.108 --> 00:53:49.925
       SOMEONE STOP HIM !

726
00:54:01.272 --> 00:54:04.172
MY SON. THIS IS MADNESS.

727
00:54:04.242 --> 00:54:06.091
     (Slynt) PUT HIM DOWN !

728
00:54:12.833 --> 00:54:15.216
DON'T LOOK !
    LET ME GO ! LET ME GO !

729
00:54:15.286 --> 00:54:17.886
       SHUT YOUR MOUTH !
       LOOK AT ME ! LOOK AT ME !

730
00:54:17.955 --> 00:54:20.405
     STOP ! DADDY ! STOP !

731
00:54:20.474 --> 00:54:22.407
NO ! NO !
      (Crowd) TRAITOR !

732
00:54:22.476 --> 00:54:23.758
         (Sansa) STOP !

733
00:54:27.431 --> 00:54:29.214
       STOP HIM ! STOP !

734
00:54:31.636 --> 00:54:33.318
       (Clamoring fades)

735
00:54:33.387 --> 00:54:35.187
       (Breathes slowly)

736
00:54:58.345 --> 00:54:59.444
       (Wings fluttering)
